            "id": 6131759,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉受美股激勵衝高 大漲逾300點刷出24570點歷史新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股昨 (28) 日在輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 及 GDP 驚喜助攻下，標普及<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>創高，同步帶動台股今 (29) 日勁揚，早盤大漲逾 300 點，最高漲至 24570.15 點，再創歷史新高點，預估成交量 4700 億元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6131759/l/b0a1b5fe0923d439b3399a228c2553b4.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉受美股激勵衝高 大漲逾300點刷出24570點歷史新高。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今天走揚，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 小漲 0.24%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲 0.36%。另外，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 小漲 0.14% 表態，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 漲 0.94%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 漲勢較爲凌厲，漲逾 3%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達近日宣布推出全新 AI 機器人大腦 Jetson AGX Thor，並公布首波 20 家合作夥伴，益登 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3048:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3048\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3048-TW</a>) 及宜鼎因入列其中，今天續揚，益登強攻漲停鎖住 38.25 元，宜鼎也有超過 2% 的漲幅。此外，聯強 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2347-TW</a>) 雖未入列合作夥伴，但根據輝達官網顯示，也拿下中國與台灣的代理權，今天同樣大漲逾半根停板。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>PCB 族群今天表現亮眼，銘旺科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2429:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2429\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2429-TW</a>) 漲停鎖住 92.1 元，精成科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6191:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6191\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6191-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，進逼漲停板，金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>)、台燿 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6274-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>) 皆有 1 至 2% 的漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股四大指數全數收紅，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲 71.67 或 0.16%，收 45636.9 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數上漲 115.019 點或 0.53%，收 21705.158 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a> 指數上漲 20.46 點或 0.32%，收 6501.86 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數上漲 28.44 點或 0.49%，收 5853.05 點。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
